1. --start-polecat=<name>: Explicit polecat selection by name
2. --start-preference: Selection preference (any|newest|oldest|cleanest)
3. --start --naked interaction: --start takes precedence with warning
4. Fix dry-run output to indicate idle polecat behavior
5. Add metrics (reuse=true) to track idle polecat reuse rate

